                        <interp inst="t18491029-name-169" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD FUNNELL</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-policeman</hi>, 32). I took Rye, and found 31<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. on him. <hi rend="largeCaps">RYE</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18491029-1867-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18491029-1867-verdict-1" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18491029-1867-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 14.—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18491029-1867-punishment-14" type="punishmentDescription">
